(firstQuint)Esteem New Subject Enrollment Post Approval Study.

 Purpose: To evaluate the long-term safety and efficacy of the Esteem Totally Implantable Hearing System (hereafter called Esteem) in subjects suffering from moderate to severe hearing loss.

 Questions: The following questions are to be answered: - Is Esteem effective through 1 year follow-up? - Is Esteem safe through 1 year follow-up? - Is the incidence of facial paresis/paralysis at 1 month follow-up no greater than 7%?.

